reviews.text: Nice and comfortable interior. Relaxing environment. Food are nicely presented and well prepared. Price is a bit on the mid to higher end but is amongst average in similar restaurants in Hong Kong.

First time here. Easy to find. Very high value lunch - big portion and tasty. Average HK$200 per person. The mussels in cheese sauce tastes terrific! The walnut cheese cake also couple perfectly with black coffee! Need to come back again.
Happy to find a place which serve good food even after 10pm

A classy restaurant with very homey decor. We went early in the evening so it was rather calm and no wait at all for a table. The food choices was rather extensive and the food was tasty. Service was alright, but a nice night out for some mussels/European food.
Very good price during Happy Hour.... STELLA $35 /pint 👍

스테이크가 맛있고 특히 햄버거 굳. 
점원도 친절하고 화이팅 넘치는 집이어서 즐거운 분위기 속에서 식사할 수 있었어요.

1일 4식하는 중이라 배가 부른 상태에 스테이크랑 햄버거 맥주 3잔만 시켰는데.. 869달러 나왔습니다. 가격이 쫌 ㅠ..

그래도 잘 먹고 왔습니다
